data.description: This prestigious well-equipped five-bedroom, 3 1/2 bath custom-built home in Talladega is situated on a .61 acre corner lot. The house features impressive details you'll notice as soon as you walk through the beautiful steel front double doors like towering ceilings, crown molding, tray ceilings, and a large open split-wing floor plan. The amazing kitchen area includes a Viking built-in fridge, Viking double ovens and cooktop surrounded by granite countertops and a center island. The master suit is an oasis fit for royalty and includes a relaxing jacuzzi tub. This amazing property also has two cozy fireplaces, a monstrous sized grass area, a pool with a rock waterfall, RV parking, landscape lighting, an outdoor shower, PAID solar panels, a mister system to beat the summer heat, block walls, and a central vacuum system. It also includes a separate living quarters with wet bar, entertainment center with projector and video screen.
